<template>
  <el-row v-for="(project,index) in projectList">
    <el-col :span="24">
      {{project.projectName}}
    </el-col>
  </el-row>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios'
export default {
  name: 'RoleManage',
  props: {
    msg: String
  },
  data() {
    return {
      projectList: [{projectName: 'asdfsd'}],
      projectForm: {
        projectName: '',
        proposer: '',
        checker: '',
        pm: '',
        status: ''
      }
    }
  },
  async beforeCreate(){
    const result = await axios.get('http://localhost:8080/project/list',{});
    console.log(result)
    this.projectList = result.data;
  },
  methods:{
    createProject:function(){
      axios.post('/project/create',this.projectForm).then(function(res){
        console.log(res)
      })
    },
    initFormData:function(){
      this.projectForm.projectName = '';
      this.projectForm.proposer = '';
      this.projectForm.checker = '';
      this.projectForm.pm = '';
      this.projectForm.status = '';

    }
  }


}
</script>

<!-- Add "scoped" attribute to limit CSS to this component only -->

h3 {
  margin: 40px 0 0;
}
ul {
  list-style-type: none;
  padding: 0;
}
li {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 0 10px;
}
a {
  color: #42b983;
}
</style>
